Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有声音传来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里的人的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音 难道是路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为什么会听见沙慈的声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝 莫非你在MS上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 沙慈? 在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在Gundam上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝 难道你在A-LAWS里?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把我的梦想托付给沙慈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 实现我的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 说定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有增援吗 这种情况下不能使用TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意后方 注意后方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为上校的胜利而战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体了吧 00-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压缩粒子 充填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不过 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败了 身为变革者的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限时间了吗 可是 刚才那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么 托勒密还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去路易丝身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体量子化了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam竟有连我都不知道的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你好像很慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没有Gadessa该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS部队 开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密停止炮击 Gundam各机 警戒态势
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那那小子打下几架?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近10架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放松警惕 我们现在的目的是破坏卫星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 我知道你担心父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是麻烦你驾驶Karel维修托勒密和Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Karel：作业用小型机器人，在CB主要用于Gundam的维修和改装）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Arios 已将运输艇护送至安全圈内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 你母亲没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 我去维修了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser 竟有此等性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动啊 快动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去路易丝身边 去路易丝身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了 沙慈的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 在这 在天人里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和杀害爸爸妈妈的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 他也是组织中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在他隔壁的 是沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来 是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双炉Gundam异常的机体性能 那架机体到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 伊安伤情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生命危险 十天左右就能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到路易丝的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在驾驶MS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呼喊我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她会在A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问 因为憎恨Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝的双亲是被Gundam杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们 路易丝加入了A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也一直这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与命运抗争…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把路易丝·阿勒威从A-LAWS中带回来 只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看重她的话应该能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我也杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是为把她带回来而战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是诡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗就会伤害人 路易丝也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你而战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 我和你们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷听可不是好习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还真笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接对那孩子说不就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗交给我 你只用负责说服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她从A-LAWS那里带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难保会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你挺有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是对过去的赎罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为过去 是为未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:09.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙里等我 很快就追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张照片 是您夫人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 两个月前还是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被卷进KATARON的反联邦恐怖袭击死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这里 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉宁上尉被追认为中校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中我听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在和敌人通信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但敌人中有准尉的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎关系亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 他们是杀害我家人的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给世界带来混乱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纤细的手臂 很难想象是机师的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该在A-LAWS中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们竟然会输给人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要利冯兹事先告知我们Twin Drive的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹·阿尔马克?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取00
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还投入了希林和迪万
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道利冯兹也不知道Twin Drive的性能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}{\pos(365,367)}里切拉王国 军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星武器又发射了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 里切拉的军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算削弱中东的军事实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 基地附近应该有近百万人规模的难民营
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道被牵连了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走无辜者的生命 什么统一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠这种做法 联邦政府真认为能获得和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的土地 人民 国家正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缄口令?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS使用的是太阳能发电用的 卫星轨道上的大功率激光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种大规模杀伤武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联邦总统的特令 无法无视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的士兵们全都目击了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸包不住火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多人对A-LAWS的做法存有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托你监督 贯彻执行缄口令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令吗 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 军令如山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从军规…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 和王留美取得联系了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正需要卫星武器的情报时…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星武器第二发向地面射出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是皇 通告全体人员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密外装修补完成后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用TRANS-AM进行最大加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向低轨道环上的敌人卫星武器发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速时继续对Gundam进行维修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果离开这个宙域 想见路易丝就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个请求 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次作战前绝对帮你修好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯呢 伙伴们都还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库斯洛德先生 你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他们有点事拜托我 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去见她 去见路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能留在A-LAWS里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明无关 留在这里才有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让喜欢打仗的人尽管去打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要找回 那段时光 那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种逃避现实的行为 会成为不自觉的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致这种结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走他们生命的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又要重蹈覆辙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim Arios Seravee的各太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成与托勒密动力部的直通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
