Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:34.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如陷落般 屈身蜷伏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:41.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Prototype boy 穿过明天的理想
